messages.messageBody:
I'm finally back from a longer hiatus than I expected. My isp software got corrupted and we were offline until today. That, combined with my trip to Birmingham has siderailed my online communications! argh.

So I've probably missed a lot of good talk, but I don't have time to read all the archives...I'll just dive in and try to keep up.:)
Kelly forwarded some of the LiveandLearn2004 digests, which I'm extremely grateful to read.
I thought of everyone up there, making connections all weekend. Can't wait to see you all next year!

Ren
